          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1619779797590-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> potato wedges</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and the <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven and cook for 25-30 min or until the wedges are golden and crispy – these are your <strong>smoky wedges</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1619779873528-x200.jpg",
