            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the wedges are in the oven, peel and finely slice the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into rings</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced shallot</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>sugar</strong> and <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Set aside to pickle – these are your <strong>pickled shallots</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
